    "Social media platforms are gradually implementing artificial intelligence (AI)-driven recommendation mechanisms to deliver tailor-made content for users.",
    "As the number of users on these platforms is exponentially increasing, they also contribute to increasing the metadata by sharing content they have made or modified.",
    "Users share these materials with friends or within specific online communities (Guy et al., 2010; Wang et al., 2013).",
    "Additionally, they can express their thoughts, create and share their portfolios, share their relationship status and memories, and engage in diverse virtual communities around the globe.",
    "These kinds of platforms have evolved into hubs for online-based social connectivity."
